**who —** SONY PLAYSTATION 5 · PS5 — an exereunesis sphere — the teardown

**what —** The current PlayStation pairs an 8-core AMD Zen 2 CPU with an RDNA 2 GPU and, most distinctively, a custom solid-state drive with dedicated decompression hardware that makes loading times nearly vanish. Hardware ray tracing and 3-D audio round out a clean, fast generation-nine machine.

